  "text": "NO x plays an important role in the formation of tropospheric O 3 and nitrate aerosols. The NO x emissions trend in Asia, and especially in China, has been an important topic, due to the rapid changes that have been observed in the past two decades [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Figure 8 shows the seven regional NO x emissions estimated for each source sector.",
